definitions.definition: By analogy with Wolfgang Amadeus Mozart , a musical virtuoso .
By extension, a virtuoso in any field.

main_definition: By analogy with Wolfgang Amadeus Mozart , a musical virtuoso .
secondary_definitions: By extension, a virtuoso in any field.

definitions.definition: A surname from German ; ( music ) used specifically of Wolfgang Amadeus Mozart (1756–1791), a prolific and influential composer of the Classical period .
